gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Mavericks 123, Suns 113
gameRecap.excerpt: The Mavericks defeated the Suns, 123-113. Luka Doncic recorded 41 points, 11 assists, and nine rebounds for the Mavericks, with Kyrie Irving adding 29 points, five rebounds, and three assists in the victory. Devin Booker tallied 35 points, eight assists, and five rebounds for the Suns in the losing effort. The Mavericks have won seven in a row and improve to 33-23, while the Suns fall to 33-23.
